## Monitored sources

Hermes looks daily / weekly at:

- **Shopify Admin API**: products, collections, sales KPIs, abandoned carts
- **Google Search Console**: domain SEO performance (if configured)
- **Klaviyo**: email flows, campaigns, segments, email KPIs (if configured)
- **Instagram**: @<handle> posts, engagement (read-only, no auto-publishing)
- **Theme files**: Liquid monitoring to detect regressions
- **`learnings.md`**: history of its own actions and their impact

